description:
The Expression properties element set consists of properties representing attributes and relationships of the RDA *Expression* entity.

Version: 1.0.0

P20001.label: has content type
P20001.description: Relates an expression to a categorization reflecting the fundamental form of communication in which the content is expressed and the human sense through which it is intended to be perceived.

P20002.label: has identifier for expression
P20002.description: Relates an expression to an appellation of expression that consists of a code, number, or other string, usually independent of natural language and social naming conventions, used to identify an expression.

P20003.label: has other distinguishing characteristic of expression (Deprecated)
P20003.description: Relates an expression to a characteristic, other than content type, language of expression, or date of expression, that serves to differentiate an expression from another expression of the same work. (Deprecated)

P20004.label: has date of capture
P20004.description: Relates an expression to a timespan that is associated with the recording, filming, etc., of an expression.

P20005.label: has award
P20005.description: Relates an expression to a formal recognition of excellence, etc., given by an award- or prize-granting body, for the content of an expression.

P20006.label: has language of expression
P20006.description: Relates an expression to a language used for the content of an expression.

P20007.label: has language of content (Deprecated)
P20007.description: Relates an expression to a language used to express the content of an expression. (Deprecated)

P20009.label: is adapted as motion picture expression
P20009.description: Relates an expression to a motion picture based on a source expression.

P20010.label: has note on changes in content characteristics
P20010.description: Relates an expression to a note on expression that provides information on variations in the content characteristics of expressions of parts, issues, or iterations of a diachronic work.

P20011.label: has conductor agent
P20011.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression of a musical work by leading a performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

P20012.label: has actor agent
P20012.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

P20013.label: has onscreen presenter agent
P20013.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by appearing on screen to provide contextual or background information.

P20014.label: has dancer agent
P20014.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by dancing in a musical, dramatic, etc., presentation.

P20015.label: has instructor agent
P20015.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by teaching or providing a demonstration.

P20016.label: has host agent
P20016.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by leading a program, often broadcast, that includes other guests, performers, etc.

P20017.label: has moderator agent
P20017.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by leading a program, often broadcast, where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.

P20018.label: has puppeteer agent
P20018.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by manipulating, controlling, or directing puppets or marionettes in a moving image production or a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

P20019.label: has panelist agent
P20019.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by participating in a program, often broadcast, where topics are discussed, usually with participation of experts in fields related to the discussion.

P20020.label: has instrumentalist agent
P20020.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by playing a musical instrument.

P20021.label: has commentator agent
P20021.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium.

P20022.label: has narrator agent
P20022.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, course of events, etc.

P20023.label: has storyteller agent
P20023.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by relaying a creator's original story with dramatic or theatrical interpretation.

P20024.label: has speaker agent
P20024.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by speaking words, such as a lecture, speech, etc.

P20025.label: has singer agent
P20025.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is a performer who contributes to an expression by using their voice, with or without instrumental accompaniment, to produce music.

P20026.label: has composer of expression (Deprecated)
P20026.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by adding music to a work that originally lacked it, by composing new music to substitute for original music, or by composing new music to supplement existing music. (Deprecated)

P20027.label: has surveyor (Deprecated)
P20027.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression of a cartographic work by providing measurements or dimensional relationships for a geographic area represented. (Deprecated)

P20028.label: has animator agent
P20028.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings.

P20029.label: has arranger agent of music
P20029.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression of a work by rewriting a composition for a medium of performance different from that for which a work was originally intended.

P20030.label: has writer of added text (Deprecated)
P20030.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression of a primarily non-textual work by providing text, such as writing captions for photographs or descriptions of maps. (Deprecated)

P20031.label: has stage director agent
P20031.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression of a stage work through the general management and supervision of a performance.

P20032.label: has interviewer agent of expression
P20032.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other agent who gathers information.

P20033.label: has draftsman agent
P20033.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by an architect, inventor, etc., by making detailed plans or drawings for buildings, ships, aircraft, machines, objects, etc.

P20034.label: has transcriber agent
P20034.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by writing down or notating unwritten or unnotated content, or by changing it from one system of notation to another.

P20035.label: has musical director agent
P20035.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by coordinating the activities of composers, sound editors, and sound mixers for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

P20036.label: has costume designer agent
P20036.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by designing costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.

P20037.label: has translator agent
P20037.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by expressing the linguistic content of the work in a language different from that of previous expressions of the original work.

P20038.label: has art director agent
P20038.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by overseeing artists and craftspeople who build sets for moving image productions.

P20039.label: has performer agent
P20039.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by performing music, acting, dancing, speaking, etc., often in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

P20040.label: has court reporter agent
P20040.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by preparing the opinions of a court for publication.

P20041.label: has writer of preface (Deprecated)
P20041.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by providing a preface to an original work. (Deprecated)

P20042.label: has cartographer of expression (Deprecated)
P20042.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by providing additional cartography, or by modifying previous cartography. (Deprecated)

P20043.label: has choreographer of expression (Deprecated)
P20043.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by providing additional choreography, or by modifying previous choreography. (Deprecated)

P20044.label: has writer of added commentary (Deprecated)
P20044.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by providing an interpretation or critical explanation of an original work. (Deprecated)

P20045.label: has writer of introduction (Deprecated)
P20045.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by providing an introduction to an original work. (Deprecated)

P20046.label: has writer of supplementary textual content (Deprecated)
P20046.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by providing supplementary textual content, such as an introduction or a preface, to an original work. (Deprecated)

P20047.label: has interviewee agent of expression
P20047.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other agent who gathers information.

P20048.label: has editor (Deprecated)
P20048.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by revising or clarifying the content, or by selecting and putting together works, or parts of works, by one or more creators. (Deprecated)

P20049.label: has abridger agent
P20049.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by shortening an expression of a related work without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.

P20050.label: has recording engineer agent
P20050.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is an audio engineer who contributes to the audio content of an expression by supervising the technical aspects of a recording session.

P20051.label: has illustrator (Deprecated)
P20051.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by supplementing the primary content with drawings, diagrams, photographs, etc. (Deprecated)

P20052.label: has recordist agent
P20052.description: Relates an expression to an agent who contributes to an expression by using a recording device to capture sound or video during a recording session, including field recordings of natural sounds, folkloric events, music, etc.

P20053.label: has creator agent of expression
P20053.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is responsible for a realization of a work.

P20054.label: has presenter agent
P20054.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is mentioned in an "X presents:" credit for moving image materials and who is probably associated with production, finance, or distribution in some way.

P20055.label: has editor agent of moving image work
P20055.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is responsible for assembling, arranging, and trimming film, video, or other moving image formats, including both visual and audio aspects.

P20056.label: has production designer agent
P20056.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is responsible for designing the overall visual appearance of a moving image production.

P20058.label: has minute taker agent
P20058.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is responsible for recording the minutes of a meeting.

P20059.label: has manifestation of expression
P20059.description: Relates an expression to a physical embodiment of an expression.

P20060.label: is adapted as radio program expression
P20060.description: Relates an expression to a radio program based on a source expression.

P20061.label: has form of tactile notation
P20061.description: Relates an expression to a set of characters or symbols used to express the content of an expression in a form that can be perceived through touch.

P20062.label: has form of notation
P20062.description: Relates an expression to a set of characters or symbols used to express the content of an expression.

P20063.label: has form of notated movement
P20063.description: Relates an expression to a set of characters or symbols used to express movement content of an expression.

P20064.label: has form of musical notation
P20064.description: Relates an expression to a set of characters or symbols used to express musical content of an expression.

P20065.label: has script
P20065.description: Relates an expression to a set of characters or symbols used to express written language content of an expression.

P20066.label: is adapted as television program expression
P20066.description: Relates an expression to a television program based on a source expression.

P20067.label: is adapted as video expression
P20067.description: Relates an expression to a video based on a source expression.

P20068.label: has writer of added lyrics (Deprecated)
P20068.description: Relates an expression to a writer of words added to an expression of a musical work. (Deprecated)

P20069.label: has summarization of content
P20069.description: Relates an expression to an abstract, summary, synopsis, etc., of the content of an expression.

P20070.label: has voice actor agent
P20070.description: Relates an expression to an agent who is an actor who contributes to an expression by providing the voice for characters in radio and audio productions and for animated characters in moving image works, as well as by providing voice-overs in radio and television commercials, dubbed expressions, etc.

P20071.label: has note on expression
P20071.description: Relates an expression to a broad unstructured description of one or more attributes of an expression.

P20073.label: is dramatized as expression
P20073.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a dramatic work adapted from a source expression.

P20074.label: is part of expression
P20074.description: Relates an expression to an expression that has another expression as a discrete component.

P20075.label: is replaced in part by expression
P20075.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content partially supersedes and renders obsolete the content of an expression of another work.

P20076.label: is replaced by expression
P20076.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content supersedes and renders obsolete the content of an expression of another work.

P20077.label: is adapted in verse as expression
P20077.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a literary composition in verse form adapted from a source expression.

P20078.label: is dubbed version of
P20078.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a moving image work in which spoken dialogue is translated into a language different from that of the original work.

P20079.label: has dubbed version
P20079.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a moving image work that translates spoken dialogue of the original work into a different language.

P20080.label: has cadenza expression
P20080.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work that consists of an ornamental passage, for a soloist, added to an expression of a musical work such as a concerto either by the same or a different composer.

P20081.label: is variations based on expression
P20081.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work from which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

P20082.label: is modified by variation as expression
P20082.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work in which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material taken from a source work forms a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

P20083.label: is cadenza composed for expression
P20083.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work, such as a concerto, to which is added an expression of musical work that is an ornamental passage for a soloist by the same or a different composer.

P20084.label: is libretto for expression
P20084.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work such as an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, that uses the text of a related work.

P20085.label: has incidental music expression
P20085.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a musical work that that provides incidental music for a play or other spoken work for the stage.

P20086.label: is remade as expression
P20086.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a motion picture, radio program, television program, or video based on an earlier work.

P20087.label: is set to music as expression
P20087.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio, that uses the text of a source work.

P20088.label: is adapted as novel expression
P20088.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a novel adapted from a source expression.

P20089.label: is appendix to expression
P20089.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content is augmented with content from an expression of a related work.

P20090.label: is abstracted in expression
P20090.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is an abstracting and indexing service that abstracts the contents of a source expression.

P20091.label: is indexed in expression
P20091.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is an abstracting and indexing service that indexes the contents of a source expression.

P20092.label: is adapted as choreography expression
P20092.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of movement based on a source work.

P20093.label: has errata expression
P20093.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of errors discovered after publication of a predominant work, with their corrections.

P20094.label: has illustrations expression
P20094.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of pictorial content designed to explain or decorate an augmented expression.

P20095.label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay expression
P20095.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of a screenplay for a motion picture, based on a source work.

P20096.label: is adapted as screenplay expression
P20096.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of a screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on a source work.

P20097.label: is adapted as television screenplay expression
P20097.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of a screenplay for a television program, based on a source work.

P20098.label: is adapted as video screenplay expression
P20098.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of a screenplay for a video, based on a source work.

P20099.label: is adapted as radio script expression
P20099.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of a script for a radio program, based on a source work.

P20100.label: is complemented by expression
P20100.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work paired with a related expression without either expression being considered to be predominate.

P20101.label: is separated into expression
P20101.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is a diachronic work that continues the partial content of another diachronic work that is continuing.

P20102.label: is screenplay for expression
P20102.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work such as a motion picture, television program, or video, that uses the text of a work as a screenplay.

P20103.label: is incidental music for expression
P20103.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work such as a play or other spoken work for the stage that uses a musical work as incidental music.

P20104.label: is abstracted as expression
P20104.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that abbreviates a source expression in a brief, objective manner.

P20105.label: is augmented by expression
P20105.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that adds to the content of a predominant expression.

P20106.label: is summarized as expression
P20106.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of a brief recapitulation of the content of a source expression.

P20107.label: has catalogue expression
P20107.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of a complete enumeration of items arranged systematically.

P20108.label: has concordance expression
P20108.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that consists of an index of all the words in a predominant expression.

P20109.label: has addenda expression
P20109.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of brief content that is essential for the completeness of an expression of a related work.

P20110.label: is adapted as libretto expression
P20110.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work consisting of the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, based on a source work.

P20114.label: is imitated as expression
P20114.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that copies the style or content of a source work.

P20115.label: is expanded as expression
P20115.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that enlarges upon the content of a source work.

P20118.label: has appendix expression
P20118.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content augments an expression of a related work.

P20119.label: is freely translated as expression
P20119.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is both an adaptation and a translation into another language of a source expression.

P20120.label: has guide expression
P20120.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that guides a user through the use of a predominant work, using notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

P20121.label: is abridgement of expression
P20121.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is shortened as an expression of a related work without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.

P20122.label: is abstract of expression
P20122.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is abstracted, i.e., abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.

P20123.label: is dramatization of expression
P20123.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a drama.

P20124.label: is verse adaptation of expression
P20124.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a literary composition in verse form.

P20125.label: is motion picture adaptation of expression
P20125.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a motion picture.

P20126.label: is novelization of expression
P20126.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a novel.

P20127.label: is radio adaptation of expression
P20127.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a radio program.

P20128.label: is television adaptation of expression
P20128.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a television program.

P20129.label: is screenplay based on expression
P20129.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video.

P20130.label: is motion picture screenplay based on expression
P20130.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a screenplay for a motion picture.

P20131.label: is television screenplay based on expression
P20131.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a screenplay for a television program.

P20132.label: is video screenplay based on expression
P20132.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as a screenplay for a video.

P20133.label: is radio script based on expression
P20133.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted as the script for a radio program.

P20134.label: is video adaptation of expression
P20134.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted for video.

P20135.label: is digest of expression
P20135.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is digested, i.e., systematically and comprehensively condensed.

P20137.label: is absorption of expression
P20137.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content is incorporated in the content of an expression of another work.

P20138.label: is absorption in part of expression
P20138.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose partial content is incorporated in the content of an expression of another work.

P20139.label: is arrangement of
P20139.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is rewritten as a musical composition for a medium of performance different from that for which a work was originally intended.

P20140.label: is free translation of expression
P20140.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is adapted and translated into another language.

P20141.label: is translation of
P20141.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is translated, i.e., the text expressed in a language different from that of an original work.

P20142.label: is parodied as expression
P20142.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that imitates the style or content of a source work for comic effect.

P20143.label: is absorbed by expression
P20143.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content incorporates the content of an expression of another work.

P20144.label: is absorbed in part by expression
P20144.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content incorporates the partial content of an expression of another work.

P20145.label: has part expression
P20145.description: Relates an expression to an expression that is a discrete component of another expression.

P20146.label: is errata to expression
P20146.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is augmented by a list of errors in a predominant work, discovered after publication, with their corrections.

P20147.label: is guide to expression
P20147.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is augmented by a related work consisting of material to help the user of a predominant work, such as notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

P20148.label: is illustrations for expression
P20148.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is augmented by pictorial content designed to explain or decorate it.

P20149.label: is continuation of expression
P20149.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is a completed diachronic work whose content is continued by an expression of another diachronic work.

P20151.label: is supplement to expression
P20151.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is updated or otherwise complemented by an augmenting expression.

P20152.label: is adaptation of expression
P20152.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is modified for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

P20153.label: is adapted as expression
P20153.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work based on a source expression.

P20154.label: is preceded by expression
P20154.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that precedes, that is, is earlier in time or before in narrative, etc., a succeeding expression.

P20155.label: has finding aid expression
P20155.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides a guide to the organization, arrangement, and contents of an archival collection.

P20156.label: has index expression
P20156.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of a predominant expression, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

P20157.label: has screenplay expression
P20157.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for a motion picture, television program or video.

P20158.label: has motion picture screenplay expression
P20158.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for a motion picture.

P20159.label: is musical setting of expression
P20159.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio.

P20160.label: has radio script expression
P20160.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for a radio program.

P20161.label: has television screenplay expression
P20161.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for a television program.

P20162.label: has video screenplay expression
P20162.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for a video.

P20163.label: has libretto expression
P20163.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that provides text for an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

P20164.label: is paraphrased as expression
P20164.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that restates the content of a source work in a different form.

P20165.label: is arranged as
P20165.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that rewrites a musical composition for a medium of performance different from that for which a work was originally intended.

P20166.label: is abridged as expression
P20166.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that shortens an expression of a related work without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.

P20167.label: is split from expression
P20167.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is a diachronic work that is completed whose partial content is continued by an expression of another diachronic work.

P20168.label: is separated from expression
P20168.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that is a diachronic work whose partial content is continued by an expression of another diachronic work.

P20169.label: is succeeded by expression
P20169.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that succeeds, that is, is later in time or after in a narrative, etc., a preceding expression.

P20170.label: is digested as expression
P20170.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that systematically and comprehensively condenses a source expression.

P20171.label: is translated as
P20171.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that translates the text of a source expression into a language different from that of an original work.

P20172.label: has supplement expression
P20172.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that updates or otherwise complements a predominant expression.

P20173.label: is screenplay for motion picture expression
P20173.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a motion picture.

P20174.label: is screenplay for television program expression
P20174.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a television program.

P20175.label: is screenplay for video expression
P20175.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a video.

P20176.label: is script for radio program expression
P20176.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work that uses the text as a script for a radio program.

P20177.label: is addenda to expression
P20177.description: Relates an expression to an expression of a work whose content is completed with brief content from an expression of a related work.

P20179.label: is summary of expression
